list.abstract: multiple是LV旗下的经典钱夹。MULTIPLE短夹钱包采用Monogram帆布制造，设有多个口袋。

yingyinNormal.en: Have we talked about the possibility of multiple births?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们谈过多胞胎的可能吗？
狂怒，同类相食，导致多人死亡。

yingyinNormal.en: You've missed multiple ship dates, and meanwhile, IBM is just purring along.
yingyinNormal.zh: 并且误了交工日期，而在这个时候，IBM正高兴得到处喵喵叫

yingyinNormal.en: Samaritan has preempted multiple threats to national security. You're welcome, Senator.
yingyinNormal.zh: 撒马利亚人预先解除了多起对国家安全的威胁。不用谢，参议员。

yingyinNormal.en: You stated that it was a dual engine failure due to multiple bird strikes? That would be unprecedented.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说因遭飞鸟多次撞击造成双发停车？这是前所未有的情况。

yingyinNormal.en: Multiple airports, runways, two successful landings. We are simply mimicking what the computer already told us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 多个机场、跑道，2起成功降落，我们只是重复下计算机的演算结果。

yingyinNormal.en: Skipping one day of school isn't gonna do any harm. I ditched plenty, and look at me today. I am fielding multiple job offers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 逃一天课不会怎么样的。我就逃了很多课，看看我现在，我得到了很多工作机会。

yingyinNormal.en: It turns out, after multiple studies were analyzed and compared, paper towels came out victorious. Why? A lot of it has to do with timing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 经过多次的研究分析比较，结果竟然是纸巾胜出。为什么呢？其实这和"时间"很有关系。

yingyinNormal.en: In multiple choice there are always the answers that are close, but then there's the correct answer and as soon as you hear it, you know it's right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 单选题中总是有相近的选项，但是有一个正确答案，一旦你听到，你就知道就是它。

yingyinNormal.en: So you're proposing that the self is an illusion, and that we actually have multiple centers of consciousness that are communicating with one another?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你是在说自我只是幻觉，人其实有多个意识中心它们在相互交流吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Like genealogists, modern linguists try to map this process by tracing multiple languages back as far as they can to their common ancestor, or protolanguage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 系谱学家、现代语言学家等试图重现这个过程，他们尽力追溯不同语言的共同的起源，也称为原始母语。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Then I bought <highlight>multiple</highlight> items of the same style in different shades.

examination_example.sentence: This means that if you give people <highlight>multiple</highlight> opportunities to lie for their own benefit, they start with little lies which get bigger over time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这意味着，如果给受试者诸多为自身利益而撒谎的机会，他们一开始会撒个小谎，随着时间的推移，谎言会越来越大。

examination_example.sentence: Well, it actually seems that <highlight>multiple</highlight> presentation formats, especially if one of them is visual, help most people learn.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 其实，多样化的呈现形式在人们学习时帮助很大，尤其是视觉呈现形式。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Multiples</highlight> can be deployed in combination for more complex missions than could be achieved by one CubeSat alone.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 多个卫星可以组合运用，以执行比一个立方体卫星更复杂的任务。

examination_example.sentence: A woman of color concerned about income inequality and programs that promote mobility by definition is a single mom, probably with <highlight>multiple</highlight> kids.

examination_example.sentence: Employees with a growth mindset may be more likely to devise innovative ideas that bridge <highlight>multiple</highlight> areas of knowledge to achieve better solutions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 具有成长型思维的员工更有可能设计出创新的想法，将多个知识领域连接起来，以得到更好的解决方案。

examination_example.sentence: What should children do to deal with <highlight>multiple</highlight> assignments?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 孩子们应该如何处理多个作业？

examination_example.sentence: The concept has <highlight>multiple</highlight> forms, and scholars and policymakers argue about the shape, scope and cost of the ideal program.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这一概念有多种形式，学者和决策者对理想计划的形式、范围和成本存在争议。
